Thank you \nIn order to better improve this application, we look forward to you taking the time out of your busy schedule to give us feedback on the suggestions and issues you have encountered during use.
APP info Use the world\'s strongest open-source audio and video library FFmpeg on your phone. \nThe current version of the audio and video editor supports functions such as executing ffmpeg command line , video format conversion, video duration and image cropping, video speed adjustment , extracting audio and video noise reduction, and obtaining audio and video information.
